  "detailed_description": "<h1>New DLC Available</h1><p></p><br><h1>READY FOR ACTION NOW? PICK UP THE ORIGINAL, SERIAL CLEANER</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1337920/extras/eb082f62bdc6240ef42896e0813175c8.avif?t=1689098124\" width=616 height=339 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1337920/extras/ac10b1d5f10b5d312769212f46f509c0.webp?t=1689098124\" width=616 height=55 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1337920/extras/b2f28ef33da06a385d4d9d3d06032a4a.poster.avif?t=1689098124\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1337920/extras/b2f28ef33da06a385d4d9d3d06032a4a.webm?t=1689098124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1337920/extras/b2f28ef33da06a385d4d9d3d06032a4a.mp4?t=1689098124\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Get rid of the bodies, make the place spotless, and don't get caught.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1337920/extras/0645435db21dc7bab7514f82f3a20aba.webp?t=1689098124\" width=616 height=55 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1337920/extras/bf2714c87a8e3e2ff1cabf2cf55ac825.poster.avif?t=1689098124\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1337920/extras/bf2714c87a8e3e2ff1cabf2cf55ac825.webm?t=1689098124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1337920/extras/bf2714c87a8e3e2ff1cabf2cf55ac825.mp4?t=1689098124\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Plan every step and move like a ghost or trust your reflexes and thrive in chaos. The choice is yours.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1337920/extras/e74b72571598ac680abf2ffc8c92de35.webp?t=1689098124\" width=616 height=55 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1337920/extras/afe620fc61106040db813ddfabd6da97.poster.avif?t=1689098124\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1337920/extras/afe620fc61106040db813ddfabd6da97.webm?t=1689098124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1337920/extras/afe620fc61106040db813ddfabd6da97.mp4?t=1689098124\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Alternate between four characters, each with a unique skill set, opening up new possibilities.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1337920/extras/2feff84f5f4cc12f5076d2eff1845b05.webp?t=1689098124\" width=616 height=55 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1337920/extras/2a683cc4cce86d1a0725daaab4d53e11.poster.avif?t=1689098124\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1337920/extras/2a683cc4cce86d1a0725daaab4d53e11.webm?t=1689098124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1337920/extras/2a683cc4cce86d1a0725daaab4d53e11.mp4?t=1689098124\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Serial Cleaners’ setting—inspired by cult ‘90s movies—will bring back fond memories of the more carefree decade full of brightly colored optimism... and the grime underneath it all.</strong>",
